lationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> First of all let me say that I'm not necessarily getting involved in this discussion, but I'd like to make an important point. Any high elf wizard (or any elf for that matter) who chooses to worship Solusek or back him up in this discussion is pretty much an idiot. You have to remember that it was Solusek himself that destroyed the great Elven empire. So I think that all elves should agree with me in saying that Solusek must pay for his actions and that all elves' ultimate goal should be to destroy the bastard. I hate you Solusek. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=eaminwhitefalcon>Eamin Whitefalcon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>¡Viva la inquisición!</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 11:43:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://chuma.cas.usf.edu/~dking3/Eamin_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> Silence, dolt! Solusek Ro, the One Above All, transcends such petty divisions as good and evil. He destroyed Takish`Hiz to preserve the balance, and you dare visit your puny anger upon him? You shall pay most dearly for your sins! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uatelen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Atelen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.com/Paris/LeftBank/4815/pics/dinovisn.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Gold Medal in the<BR>Distance Gnome Punt</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 11:54:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> Actually, some of the elves saw the power of Solusek, and also saw that the destruction of Takish Hiz was necessary, and therefore chose to follow him. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=284584" target="_blank">
