</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 6:21:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/neriakwraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  He destroyed Takish`Hiz to preserve the balance<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
 <br>
The lore from beta says Solusek Ro was angered with the Gods of Power and Influence for punishing his son (Rallos Zek) and his creations for their attack on the Plane of Earth.<br>
<br>
That is the only mention of why he did it.<br>
<br>
Personally, I think he did it to create a market for beachfront property. The orcs seem to like it there <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A> at: 8/8/02 6:22:35 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=eaminwhitefalcon>Eamin Whitefalcon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>¡Viva la inquisición!</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 6:45:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://chuma.cas.usf.edu/~dking3/Eamin_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> Which is one instance where the lore is wrong. Rallos Zek isn't Solusek Ro's son. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 8:25:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/neriakwraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Which is one instance where the lore is wrong. Rallos Zek isn't Solusek Ro's son.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Eamin, why Solusek Ro raised the Serpent Mountains, which resulted in the last Elven city on Tunaria being destroyed?<br>
<br>
A. He did it as a direct move against Tunare<br>
<br>
B. He did it because he wanted to make his mark on Norrath<br>
<br>
C. He did it because he felt like it, and didn't care about the resulting destruction<br>
<br>
D. He did it because the elven race was gaining too much power<br>
<br>
E. Other<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=eaminwhitefalcon>Eamin Whitefalcon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>¡Viva la inquisición!</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 8:32:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://chuma.cas.usf.edu/~dking3/Eamin_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> I do not attempt to understand His Holy Motives, but I'd have to go with D. Whether the elves were on the side of good (as I maintain) or on the side of evil (as you maintain) at the time is irrelevant, as either way the balance would be upset if they were aloud to conquer more territories and destroy those of the opposite alignment. By crushing a strongly aligned empire before it could do more damage, Solusek Ro championed the cause of neutrality. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 8:52:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=32>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/neriakwraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> I'd probably go with D too Eamin, but it has everything to do with the corruption of the Elven Empire by Innoruuk. <br>
<br>
At the time that Solusek Ro raised the Serpent mountains, the war between the loyalist elves and the rebel elves was almost over, with the loyalists being pushed back into Faydwer by the rebels. The rebels had already taken all of the tunarian outposts and cities, and it seemed like the loyalist Innoruuk worshippers would be wiped out by the rebels.<br>
<br>
So, in order to maintain balance between the two, Solusek Ro created his desert of Ro, which caused the destruction of the rebel city of Takish`Hiz. That act possibly allowed the Elven loyalists to escape into the Underfoot of Norrath, and eventually establish Neriak.<br>
<br>
So in a way, Solusek was acting against Tunare and with Innoruuk to preserve balance.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I do not attempt to understand His Holy Motives<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
Ignorance is never an acceptible answer by the way <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=eaminwhitefalcon>Eamin Whitefalcon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>¡Viva la inquisición!</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 8:56:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://chuma.cas.usf.edu/~dking3/Eamin_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> When you're a zealot it is.<br>
<br>
It could be your way, or it could be that Solusek Ro wanted to get the light elves further away from Neriak so they wouldn't eradicate the Teir`Dal.<br>
Either way, it shows the Great Lord being an All-Wise, All-Merciful, All-Knowing, and All-Powerful deity. Hail Solusek Ro! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/8/02 10:09:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=34>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/neriakwraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sol Ro...</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> It could be your way, or it could be that Solusek Ro wanted to get the light elves further away from Neriak so they wouldn't eradicate the Teir`Dal.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Neriak <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> didn't exist</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> when Takish`Hiz fell. In fact, the capital of the Loyalist (inny worshippers) Empire was Caerthiel, which was located in the Loping Plains on Faydwer. <br>
<br>
The loyalist Emperor was assassinated during the battle of Aerignon, which forced the Loyalists to retreat into the underfoot of Norrath. The Rebels destroyed Caerthiel in a fit of rage, and then built Felwithe on the place where the Loyalist Emperor was slain, just north of Elizerain lake.<br>
<br>
The loyalists returned to the surface and retreated to Antonica, building Neriak in the forest of Nektulos. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showPrevMessage?topicID=292.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showNextMessage?topicID=292.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.emailToFriend?topicID=292.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.threadControl?topicID=292.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=292.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm38.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=292.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm41">Interface Design